Ranger Help for: wrath of gaia
================================

SYNTAX:      wrath <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   10
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to call upon Gaia's wrath, unleashing a
powerful nature damage attack against a target. The earth itself
rises against the Ranger's enemy. The damage is terrain-based and
deals significantly more damage when the Ranger is fighting in their
primary terrain. This is one of the most powerful offensive spells
available to a Ranger and costs a great deal of spell points to use.
The damage scales with wisdom and guild level.
